comments: Williams Jr. (MEM) briefly engages and disengages with Coffey (LAC) following the pick.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) leans into Mann (LAC), but the contact is marginal.
Coffey (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position during Kennard's (MEM) drive to the basket.
Harden (LAC) cleanly dislodges the ball from Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) possession and the ensuing contact to the arm is incidental.
Kennard (MEM) swipes down and avoids making contact with Coffey's (LAC) arm during Coffey's driving shot attempt.

After Coffey (LAC) gathers to start his upward shooting motion, he brings his right hand toward Kennard's face. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Mann (LAC) places his hands on Jackson's (MEM) lower body with slight extension, but the contact is marginal and does not dislodge him from his rebounding position.
Zubac (LAC) reaches in and initiates contact with Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) arm after his gather, affecting his driving shot attempt.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) goes to, not through, Leonard's (LAC) space, and marginal contact occurs as Jackson Jr. releases away during the drive.
Leonard (LAC) brings his left hand forward and makes contact with the ball when Jackson Jr. (MEM) steps into his upward shooting motion.
Williams Jr. (MEM) commits a take foul on George (LAC).
Williams (MEM) commits a take foul on Leonard (LAC).
